snippet.title: Cat Quest - Android Launch Trailer - Android
snippet.description:
Cat Quest, the most pawsome RPG ever, is out on Android on September 15th!

Find out more at:
https://www.facebook.com/catquestgame/
https://thegentlebros.com/catquest/

Follow us on Twitter @TheGentlebros
https://twitter.com/TheGentlebros

Subscribe to the mailing list and get notified when it releases!
https://thegentlebros.com/catquest/#subscribe

Gameplay shown was captured using the Android version of Cat Quest!
